public interface HTMLElement
extends Element

All HTML element interfaces derive from this class. Elements that only exposethe HTML core attributes are represented by the base HTMLElement interface. These elements are as follows:HEAD special: SUB, SUP, SPAN, BDOfont: TT, I, B, U, S, STRIKE, BIG, SMALL phrase: EM, STRONG, DFN, CODE, SAMP, KBD, VAR, CITE, ACRONYM, ABBRlist: DD, DTNOFRAMES, NOSCRIPTADDRESS, CENTER Note. The style attribute for thisinterface is reserved for future usage.
